{
  "video_id": "jTT5wrAORF0",
  "title": "How ‘A Quiet Place’ Kept Quiet | Anatomy of a Scene",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 499.0,
      "end_time": 1640.0,
      "text": "This is John Krasinski,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1640.0,
      "end_time": 6449.0,
      "text": "the director and one of the actors in “A Quiet Place.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6449.0,
      "end_time": 7590.0,
      "text": "What you’re watching now is"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7590.0,
      "end_time": 9660.0,
      "text": "at the very beginning of the movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9660.0,
      "end_time": 12930.0,
      "text": "This is our hero family walking home"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12930.0,
      "end_time": 16679.0,
      "text": "from a — now established as an abandoned town."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16679.0,
      "end_time": 19220.0,
      "text": "And this sort of sets up a lot of the rules of the movie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 19220.0,
      "end_time": 20636.0,
      "text": "one of which you’re seeing right here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 20636.0,
      "end_time": 22602.0,
      "text": "which is the idea of perspective and sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 22602.0,
      "end_time": 24440.0,
      "text": "[light footsteps]"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 24440.0,
      "end_time": 26100.0,
      "text": "When we’re close up on something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 26100.0,
      "end_time": 26970.0,
      "text": "you can really hear it."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 26970.0,
      "end_time": 28511.0,
      "text": "And then when you go to a wider shot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 28511.0,
      "end_time": 30390.0,
      "text": "you can’t hear that exact same sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 30390.0,
      "end_time": 32490.0,
      "text": "which is one of the things we really loved doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 32490.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34500.0,
      "text": "throughout the whole movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 34500.0,
      "end_time": 36239.0,
      "text": "We shot this film in Upstate New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 36240.0,
      "end_time": 39390.0,
      "text": "The idea was to be in a very rural area in sort"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 39390.0,
      "end_time": 42730.0,
      "text": "of a post-apocalyptic time to feel isolation."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 42730.0,
      "end_time": 44489.0,
      "text": "And so being in the middle of nowhere"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 44490.0,
      "end_time": 46949.0,
      "text": "helps this family feel like they’re in the middle of nowhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 46990.0,
      "end_time": 48840.0,
      "text": "And it adds tension, I think, to the fact that"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 48840.0,
      "end_time": 51240.0,
      "text": "they have nowhere to turn or nobody around them to help them."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 52830.0,
      "end_time": 54460.0,
      "text": "Sound design in this is huge."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 54460.0,
      "end_time": 57570.0,
      "text": "It’s totally a main character that is right along"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 57570.0,
      "end_time": 58780.0,
      "text": "here with the family."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 58780.0,
      "end_time": 62660.0,
      "text": "So Millie, one of the actresses, is a deaf actress."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 62660.0,
      "end_time": 65758.0,
      "text": "And we’re about to do one of my favorite things in the movie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 65759.0,
      "end_time": 67200.0,
      "text": "which is play with her perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 67200.0,
      "end_time": 69170.0,
      "text": "We wanted the sound of the movie to"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 69270.0,
      "end_time": 71400.0,
      "text": "reflect her own actual experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 71400.0,
      "end_time": 73620.0,
      "text": "So you can hear sound when you’re walking with Emily and I, like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 75520.0,
      "end_time": 76985.0,
      "text": "and with Noah."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 76985.0,
      "end_time": 79210.0,
      "text": "[light footsteps]"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 79210.0,
      "end_time": 81820.0,
      "text": "And then right here, you cut to Millie, and we pull sound out."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 84149.0,
      "end_time": 86440.0,
      "text": "So we’re in “the envelope,\" we called it — the envelope"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 86440.0,
      "end_time": 90310.0,
      "text": "being in her head, she can hear very little thanks"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 90310.0,
      "end_time": 91570.0,
      "text": "to a hearing aid that she has."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 91570.0,
      "end_time": 93922.0,
      "text": "But she can’t hear much of anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 93922.0,
      "end_time": 96130.0,
      "text": "And so we play with that throughout the entire movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 96130.0,
      "end_time": 98470.0,
      "text": "So she can’t tell that there’s a sound being"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 98470.0,
      "end_time": 99940.0,
      "text": "made behind her right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 99940.0,
      "end_time": 101980.0,
      "text": "And so this is her perspective — seeing me run,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 101980.0,
      "end_time": 104410.0,
      "text": "seeing me look scared, but she doesn’t know why."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 104410.0,
      "end_time": 105922.0,
      "text": "And then she realizes right here."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 105922.0,
      "end_time": 108130.0,
      "text": "And when she realizes is that her little brother just"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 108130.0,
      "end_time": 110630.0,
      "text": "made the first big sound of the movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 110630.0,
      "end_time": 115390.0,
      "text": "And you can see that that sound has horrible consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 115390.0,
      "end_time": 118740.0,
      "text": "[music]"
    }
  ]
}